## Unit 6 Lessons > Days 5 
 
#### Concepts Covered  
Build the base of the robot.
 
#### Lesson Overview 
Groups of students will get their box/kit and pull out the manual start going through the steps on p. 8-21 with your students to make sure they understand the format of the manual, be able to follow the instructions in order to build the base of the robot.
<br><br> 
 
